      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in impeccable condition. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a recalibrated double VANOS system for peak volumetric efficiency. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via a variable M-Differential. The chassis is structurally superior, having undergone proactive subframe reinforcement and a full suspension refresh with OEM bushings to maintain factory kinematics. Finished in Carbon Black with a flawless clear coat, the car exhibits zero mechanical or aesthetic defects. Extensive service records validate its mechanical integrity, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is met with absolute confidence.",
