    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2019 BMW M2 Competition in Hockenheim Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and shows as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. The shadow-line trim remains deep black without any UV fading. Inside, the black Dakota leather with blue contrast stitching is pristine; the seat bolsters show zero wear, and the carbon fiber trim is free of any scratches or delamination. Mechanically, this M2 is perfect. It has a full documented service history exclusively through BMW authorized centers, including the critical 1,200-mile break-in service. The tires are the original Michelin Pilot Super Sports with over 80% tread remaining. This car has never seen a track, has never been modified, and has never been driven in the rain. Sale includes both original keys, the factory window sticker, and all service receipts. This is a collector-grade example for a discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 44900.0,
